ad\n    69\t    When the user runs \"run history\"\n    70\t    Then the command fails with error containing \"does not exist\"\n    71\t\n    72\t  # SC-RUN-010\n    73\t  Scenario: Runtime log write failures do not affect durable history\n    74\t    Given runtime log writes are failing\n    75\t    When durable history is queried via \"run history\"\n    76\t    Then durable history records are returned intact\n    77\t    And no durable history records are fabricated, removed, or reordered\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
